# VISION-FLIXğŸ˜





**VISION-FLIX** ek modern **movie aur TV show streaming platform** hai, inspired by Netflix. Ye project users ko **movies aur shows browse, search, aur watch** karne ka interactive interface provide karta hai.

---

## ğŸ”¥ Features

- **Responsive Design:** Desktop aur mobile devices dono ke liye optimized.
- **Browse & Search:** Movies aur TV shows easily search aur filter kar sakte hain.
- **Movie Details:** Har movie/show ke liye description, rating, genre aur trailer link.
- **Watchlist/Favorites:** Users apne favorite movies add kar sakte hain.
- **Modern Tech Stack:**  
  - Frontend: React, Vite  
  - Backend: Node.js, Express  
  - Database: MongoDB  

